A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Article 1 of Chapter 2A of Title 31 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
2 relating to the Department of Public Health generally, so as to establish an Infant Wellness
3 Resource hotline service; to provide for the development and dissemination of materials
4 promoting such hotline service; to provide for the development and implementation of
5 training for staff of such hotline service; to provide for the Department of Administrative
6 Services to select healthcare professionals to deliver healthcare services via telehealth
7 through such hotline service; to provide certain persons participating in the activities of such
8 hotline service with immunity from civil and criminal liability; to authorize rules and
9 regulations; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
11 SECTION 1.
12 Article 1 of Chapter 2A of Title 31 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to the
13 Department of Public Health generally, is amended by adding a new Code section to read as
14 follows:
15 "31-2A-21.
16 (a) As used in this Code section, the term:
